{"tid":1666479,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"清真寺改「中国化」 中共干部威脅 :「不聽話消滅你」","createTime":"2019-10-21T04:05:26.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-21T10:17:07.000Z","uid":184679,"like":13,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"9975c9f452a2cd5d5eeb5e91b651b19fd741fd08","tid":1666479,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T04:05:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/liveNews/BigPic/600_phpYbHND7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2FliveNews%2FBigPic%2F600_phpYbHND7.jpg&h=d3c6d5da&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n中國陝西省定邊縣1座清真寺頂端的月牙、洋蔥頭式尖頂及塔式建築全遭拆除，甚至原本桃形的門窗都被改為方形。（圖擷取自《寒冬》雜誌）<br />\n<br />\n中共強力打壓宗教，除了嚴密監控新疆地區，更秘密通過「伊斯蘭教中國化5年計劃（2018-2022）」，不惜耗資上百萬元人民幣大肆破壞數百年歷史的清真寺，進行「中國化」改造，引發信徒、學者撻伐。<br />\n<br />\n長期關注中國人權議題的《寒冬》雜誌揭露，中國陝西省定邊縣1座清真寺5月中旬遭改建，清真寺頂端的月牙、洋蔥頭式尖頂及塔式建築全遭拆除，甚至原本桃形的門窗都被改為方形。河南平頂山市、新鄉市8座清真寺的圓頂、新月標誌7月被拆。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/liveNews/BigPic/600_phpkbqCNJ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2FliveNews%2FBigPic%2F600_phpkbqCNJ.jpg&h=b0417d48&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n中國河南平頂山市1座清真寺的圓頂、新月標誌7月被中共拆除。（圖擷取自《寒冬》雜誌）<br />\n<br />\n青海省1名阿訇（學者）透露，政府還要求信眾進行政治培訓，並在信教群眾間傳播，以此滲透「習思想」。不少阿訇也無奈說：<span style=\"color: red;\">「現在清真寺裡裝有監控器，我們一舉一動都在公安局的監控中，如果不按照政府的意思講經就會遭罰。」</span><br />\n<br />\n報導指出，新鄉市1位政府官員威脅當地穆斯林：「56個民族1個也不能掉隊，都得聽共產黨的，不聽共產黨的就把你消滅，哪個民族和共產黨鬧事，說消滅你，就把你消滅掉。」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/liveNews/BigPic/600_phpvR5o0u.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2FliveNews%2FBigPic%2F600_phpvR5o0u.jpg&h=003f5d4d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n中國新疆維吾爾族自治區喀什市的街道上，一處大螢幕正播放國家主席習近平的談話。（法新社）<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/2930822\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F2930822&d=IZFSAkWTwbXSesVVmoeERZBhszO9bAnYmyMPTpIehd8%3D&h=fb934355\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F2930822&h=182b9db2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/2930822</a>"},{"pid":"7a52250f407966f4921f061a41f620a55ebe2f4c","tid":1666479,"uid":172638,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T04:08:26.000Z","msg":"提大家今日有咩活動 10 &middot; 21<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n-----------------------------------------------------------------<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong>12:30 醫民同行 醫護抗暴 靜坐行動</strong></span> <br />\n- 八間醫院<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong>19:00 - 23:00 毋忘721 元朗恐襲三個月靜坐</strong></span><br />\n- 18區黨鐵站大堂<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong>#39mRunFor721 全港和理跑</strong></span><br />\n- [時間地點不限 跑步計時39分鐘]"},{"pid":"4788083e1faf900105e372a08b41c9d2bd55dfa2","tid":1666479,"uid":47605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T04:08:39.000Z","msg":"不如全港黨鐵靜坐聲討721啦<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <a href=\"https://lih.kg/1665580\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1665580</a> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0394bc2b8dd684b7a30372c0f9b8e371fa38684a","tid":1666479,"uid":1082,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T04:09:57.000Z","msg":"不如索性唔好叫真主呀拉，直接改埋叫真主呀平啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/04.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/04.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/04.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/04.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c06588a4e9425e8900809068b71762e36523d8fe","tid":1666479,"uid":93986,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T04:11:05.000Z","msg":"香港人呢？消滅？"},{"pid":"f3ee6ae134cf07ba5ff682ed54058c734bf0d337","tid":1666479,"uid":320943,"